-- Ignatiev Says Ruble Decline May Affect January Inflation Level
-- B y   A r t y o m   D a n i e l y a n
-- 2011-12-22T13:45:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-22/ignatiev-says-ruble-decline-may-affect-january-inflation-level.html
The ruble’s slump may affect the
inflation rate in  Russia  next month, central bank Chairman
Sergey Ignatiev said, adding that he was “surprised” by the
slow current consumer-price growth.  Political risks may already be priced into the national
currency’s rate, Ignatiev told reporters in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Artyom Danielyan in Moscow at 
